    "description": "<p>A Product Focused lighting agency rooted in Asia Pacific working internationally to offer a wide array of creative services and technical light instruments. Our expertise spans across commercial & public spaces, hospitality, and a variety of other projects — light is second nature.</p><p>We are a dynamic team comprising of creatives, planners and problem solvers capable of delivering a wide range of general and technical services in the lighting field, and behind every outstanding deliverable is a solid process that keeps us true to our overall goal - making the world a better place through the art and science of lighting. From interactive product illustrations and design support to mock-ups and installations, complex programming  to on-site maintenance. All of our services happen in-house and are focused on your goals. From the elegance of the products that we offer to the precision of execution, we are uncompromising.</p><p><br /></p><p><br /></p>",
